<p>
  CSS minification is one of the highest-ROI optimizations in web performance. A single command can reduce your stylesheet by 30–60%, cutting load times and improving Core Web Vitals scores with almost zero effort. Whether you want to <strong>minify CSS online</strong> for a quick one-off task or integrate minification into a full build pipeline, this guide covers every approach — from browser-based tools to PostCSS, Webpack, and Vite.
</p>

<p>
